<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Tile Probability & Board Position</h2>

<p>Understanding tile distribution helps you anticipate when EU combinations will appear on your rack. E appears 12 times in the standard 100-tile bag (worth 1 point), while U appears 4 times (worth 1 point). Together, the EU pair contributes 2 points before counting any other letters in your word.</p>

